repo_metadata.description: Native access to MacOS FSEvents in Node.js

owner_record.name: fsevents - Native NodeJS module for MacOSX file system events

advisories.title: Code injection in fsevents
advisories.description: fsevents before 1.2.11 depends on the https://fsevents-binaries.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com URL, which might allow an adversary to execute arbitrary code if any JavaScript project (that depends on fsevents) distributes code that was obtained from that URL at a time when it was controlled by an adversary.
